      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>This is a friendly reminder from SubMinder.</p>
        <p>
          Your subscription for <strong><%= subscriptionName %></strong> is set
          to renew in 3 days.
        </p>

        <p><strong>Renewal Date:</strong> <%= renewalDate %></p>
        <p>
          <strong>Amount:</strong>
          <span class="amount"><%= price %> <%= currency %></span>
        </p>

        <p>
          If you intended to cancel this subscription, please do so before the
          date above to avoid unwanted charges.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,<br />The SubMinder Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
